section.section:
The application form shall require the following information:
the name and address of the applicant;
the reason for desiring the requested license or permit;
if the applicant is an individual, the citizenship of the individual;
if the applicant is a partnership, association, or corporation, the names, addresses, and citizenship of the partners of the partnership or officers and directors of the association or corporation; and
proof of liability insurance in the amount that the State Fire Prevention Commission sets.
